<HEADLINE> Chinese General Meets Chief of Pakistani Navy </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, May 8 (Xinhua) -- Visiting Chinese General Yu
Yongbo, member of the Central Military Commission, called on
Pakistan's Chief of Naval Staff Admiral Fasih Bokhari at the naval
headquarters here today.
</P>
<P>
Yu Yongbo, who is also chief of the General Political
Department of the People's Liberation Army of China, discussed
with Fasih Bokhari matters of mutual interest.
</P>
<P>
Yu Yongbo arrived here Monday for a five-day official and
good-will visit. After his Pakistani tour, he will also visit
Egypt and Russia.  
</P>
