<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Chinese Vice-Premier Meets Former Australian PM </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 8 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Zhu Rongji, met
with John Fraser, former Prime Minister of Australia, here today.
</P>
<P>
They held friendly and cordial talks and expressed satisfaction
with the improvement of bilateral relations in recent years.
</P>
<P>
Fraser is here as guest of China-Australia Chamber of Commerce
to attend its trade seminar.  
</P>
