<HEADLINE> Inflation Up in Uganda </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, May 8 (Xinhua) -- The Inflation rate for April, 1997,
rose to 10 percent compared to 6.7 percent in May, reported the
local daily the New Vision today.
