the prices for staple foodstuffs was recorded in April, the paper
said.
</P>
<P>
The cost of fruits and vegetables rose by over 10 percent in most
urban areas but fish, milk, eggs, sugar, tea and spices experienced
slight price increase in April, the paper said. enditem

