<HEADLINE> Results of Dunkirk Cycling Race </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, May 7 (Xinhua) -- Following are the leading results in
the 184-kilometer second stage of the Dunkirk Four Days cycling
race at Montigny-en-Gohelle, on Wednesday:
