<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 7 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major
world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on May 8, issued by
China's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 10 degrees c., max. 25 degrees c., overcast to
clear, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 20 degrees c., max. 25 degrees c., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 29 degrees c., max. 37 degrees c., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Sydney: min. 16 degrees c., max. 23 degrees c., drizzle, clam
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Karachi: min. 24 degrees c., max. 35 degrees c., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Cairo: min. 15 degrees c., max. 28 degrees c., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Moscow: min. 10 degrees c., max. 19 degrees c., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt: min. 6 degrees c., max. 15 degrees c., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Paris: min. 6 degrees c., max. 13 degrees c., overcast, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
London: min. 4 degrees c., max. 11 degrees c., cloudy to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
New York: min. 9 degrees c., max. 19 degrees c., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.  
</P>
